RT @ABCNewsLive: Many of the 15 million Americans living with cancer are coming to terms with a pandemic that has upended support systems and coping mechanisms, facing difficult choices about how to live fully in the era of social distance.

@devindwyer has more. https://t.co/QMViiOWOI7 https://t.co/hVwKGhMJOY

text:
RT @ABCNewsLive: "Everybody deserves to be treated with humanity and dignity and respect. And in the case of Mr. Floyd, none of that happened."

Sonia Pruitt, national chairwoman for @TheRealNBPA, joins @ABCNewsLive to discuss the death of George Floyd. https://t.co/VNzNTYDPJ9 https://t.co/lQdKmM9hTC
